        "Description": "Shade wolves were [[wolves]] that had been killed and raised as shades. They were not affected by un-enchanted [[weapon]]s, and thus must be battled by other means.",
        "History": "''Circa'' the {{YearlinkName|1369}}, the village of [[Imnesvale (town)|Imnesvale]] became haunted by the [[Shade Lord]]. The evil lord used his fell [[magic]] to kill packs of wolves and invade them with his darkness. The creatures were transformed into shade wolves and used as minions in his unholy army."
